/**
 *  Name         : GMail Nice Pack
 *  Based on     : Outlook.com style for Gmail (by Volvados) @ https://userstyles.org/styles/97006/outlook-com-style-for-gmail
 *                 Pimp.my.Gmail Sidebar (by Kilroy) @ https://userstyles.org/styles/26456/pimp-my-gmail-sidebar
 *                 Gmail Easy Access Colored Buttons (by Stevesigma) @ https://userstyles.org/styles/56063/gmail-easy-access-colored-buttons
 *                 Gmail *2* small attachment icons  (by Moktoipas) @ https://userstyles.org/styles/3958/gmail-2-small-attachment-icons
 *
 *  Updated      : Nov 06, 2017
 *  Description  : Outlook.com style for Gmail. Minimalist, metro-like appearance for Gmail and Google Calendar + Mailbox Icons Sidebar + Easy Access Colored Buttons + Small attachment icons
 */
* {
    box-shadow: none !important;
    border-radius: 0px !important;
